I would like to share this source i have worked on i am not going to work on private servers for now i hope this source helps you guys
This is Hybrid pvp v3 but you will see what has been changed

I have also fixed the glitch in the zamorak boss in godwars
smooth loading bar
fixed pkp farming
clipped following
3 funpk areas
Skiller Island 20%
Castle wars 12%
Fixed Pest Control and added the Gui's ( a bit bugged)
Removed the pk timers
Fixed the corp beast not being attackable (easy fix)
Fixed tormented demons with drops (easy fix)
Added dicing
Added more bosses
fixed many nerfed weapons (Thank You Lord Anarchy)
added the required levels for vesta's morrigans etc
and much more i cant think of
Please reguard to this thread of hybrid pvp to see the other content this server brings
http://google.com/runescape-development/google/downloads/308849-hybrid-pvp-v3-dspk-602-anims-gfx-602-npcs-634-items-summoning-pets-pkp-more.html
Thank you for reading my release thread -Dextrell
Things i decided to remove Highscores Balance elemental Bork Nex Agility Shop Resizeable client Avatar of Creation Unholy Bear
Link you had your time leechers :D
Credits 42% Sanity 18% Nintendo 10% Lordy/Trivzor (Creator of Hybrid Pvp) 22% Dextrell 3% Insidia & Faris 7% Lord Anarchy
